CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 4 reads: "Heads Forum - Miss Joy Gidding is executive secretary of the Hill District People's Forum, which presented its first program of the season at the Irene Kaufmann Settlement auditorium last Tuesday. Miss Gidding is a student at Antioch College, Ohio, and is doing her practical field work at IKS. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Joy Gidding seated at desk in office, possibly Irene Kaufmann Settlement
